parameters:
...It's hot, isn't it? Shall we use the Bonfire? It's really hot
though...

Hello~. Listen to me for a moment~. Bestie Hame-chan made a
promise and broke it~! I'm really angry now. Our bond is on the
verge of crisis~. And also, there's something really
terrible~...

It seems like it's going to be a long story... Let's call it
quits around here...

\SE[2]Clearly, this place... I wonder if \SE[3]everything is
ready...?
